AD_FORM.NAME: Generate Invoices (manual)
AD_FORM.HELP: Generate Invoices from Orders. Select the orders to generate the invoice for.

AD_FORM.NAME: Generate Shipments (manual)
AD_FORM.HELP: Generate Shipments from Orders. Select the orders to generate the shipments for.

AD_FORM.NAME: POS
AD_FORM.HELP: Enter Transactions via a POS Terminal. Automatically, scans or credit card swipes are recongized.

AD_FORM.NAME: Tree Maintenance
AD_FORM.HELP: View and change trees. Maintain the entries in their specific Windows.

AD_FORM.NAME: Performance Indicators
AD_FORM.HELP: View all Performance Indicators and Goals

AD_FORM.NAME: Translation Import/Export
AD_FORM.HELP: Export/Import Translation info to/from xml for translation in external tool. Please note that the Language MUST be an enabled and verified System Langage.

AD_FORM.NAME: Import File Loader
AD_FORM.DESCRIPTION: Load flat Files into import tables
AD_FORM.HELP: The Import File Loader parses the content of a flat file and loads it into import tables. Comments start with a '[' and end with a ']' and are ignored; example: [Some Heading].

AD_FORM.NAME: Initial Client Setup
AD_FORM.HELP: Set up a new Client/Tenant of the system

AD_FORM.NAME: Generate Charges
AD_FORM.HELP: Use the upper portion to create new charges using the general charge accounts. Use the lower portion to create charges based on the natural account.

AD_FORM.NAME: Payment Selection (manual)
AD_FORM.HELP: Select vendor invoices for payment. If you don't see an invoice, make sure that it is not included in a different (nprocessed) Payment Selection.

AD_FORM.NAME: Matching PO-Receipt-Invoice
AD_FORM.DESCRIPTION: Match Purchase Orders, Receipts, Vendor Invoices
AD_FORM.HELP: Make sure that the Receipts and Invoices are processed. If you want to match partial shipment, make sure that "Same Quantity" is not selected.

AD_FORM.NAME: Merge Entities
AD_FORM.DESCRIPTION: Merge From Entity to To Entity - Delete From
AD_FORM.HELP:
Dangerous - Please are aware of what you are doing! All instances of the From entity (e.g. Customer A) are changed to the To entity (e.g. Customer B). The From entity (e.g. Customer A) is deleted.

There is NO undo nor trace ! Please do a backup first Please be aware that you may be changing history records (e.g. invoices, etc.) !

Side effects: Merging Products are likely to distort product costs; Merging Business Partners may result in incorrect open item balance. Check with support on remedies.

Restrictions: Accounting and Inventory conflicts are not resolved in this version.

AD_FORM.NAME: BOM Drop
AD_FORM.HELP: Drop the extended Bill of Materials into an Order, Invoice, etc. The documents need to be in a Drafted stage. Make sure that the items included in the BOM are on the price list of the Order, Invoice, etc. as otherwise the price will be zero!

AD_FORM.NAME: Archive Viewer
AD_FORM.HELP: Depending on the Client Automatic Archive Level documents and reports are saved and available for view. In the Report Viewer you can manually archive Documents or Reports. You can only view archives, if you have access to the original document.

AD_FORM.NAME: Product Attribute Grid
AD_FORM.DESCRIPTION: Maintain Products with Attributes in a Table Grid
AD_FORM.HELP: Select one or two attributes if a Product Attribute and display/maintain products in a row or table grid.
